537
00:40:52,158 --> 00:40:55,745
在风中染上色彩
Can you paint with all the colors

538
00:40:55,912 --> 00:40:59,499
化做云烟
Ofthe wind?

539
00:41:06,506 --> 00:41:10,343
在走进丛林不会觉得疲倦
Come run the hidden pine trails ofthe forest

540
00:41:10,510 --> 00:41:14,597
