就让风声化做歌声围绕山头
We need to sing with all the voices ofthe mountain

552
00:42:06,733 --> 00:42:11,571
在风中染上色彩化做云烟
We need to paint with all the colors ofthe wind

553
00:42:11,738 --> 00:42:14,532
你会慢慢发觉到
You can own the earth, and still

554
00:42:14,699 --> 00:42:18,244
你所拥有的一切
All you'll own is earth until

555
00:42:18,411 --> 00:42:20,705
在风中
You can paint

556
00:42:20,872 --> 00:42:23,833
染上色彩
With all the colors

557
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:27,754
化做
Ofthe

558
00:42:27,920 --> 00:42:33,926
云烟
Wind

559
00:42:48,733 --> 00:42:50,359
是什么啊？
What is it?

560
00:42:50,526 --> 00:42:53,946
鼓声  出麻烦了
The drums. They mean trouble.

561
00:42:54,113 --> 00:42:56,741
我该走了
I shouldn't be here.

562
00:42:56,908 --> 00:42:58,701
什么时候可以再见你？ 不行啊
- I want to see you again. - I can't.

563
00:42:58,868 --> 00:43:00,870
不要  不要走 很抱歉
- Please, don't leave. - I'm sorry.

564
00:43:04,123 --> 00:43:06,167
我得走了
I have to go.

565
00:43:16,469 --> 00:43:18,721
好了  这次差不多了
All right! This one's ready to hoist!

566
00:43:18,888 --> 00:43:21,307
准备好  推
Two on each side. Ready now? Push!

567
00:43:21,474 --> 00:43:23,101
小心点  有点滑
Watch it! It's slipping.

568
00:43:23,267 --> 00:43:26,229
怎么了？伙伴们 一个小事都做不好
Come on, lads, it's only a little picket fence.

569
00:43:26,395 --> 00:43:28,564
拉紧  拉紧 好了
- Steady! Steady! - There you go.

570
00:43:28,731 --> 00:43:31,150
庄哥  这样就什么也进不来了
That'll keep everything out, eh, John?

571
00:43:33,319 --> 00:43:35,655
你怎么了  庄哥？ 什么？
- Something wrong, John? - What?

572
00:43:35,822 --> 00:43:40,743
这几天你总是一句话也不说 他先前没赶上那场热闹
- You've been quiet the last few days. - He's mad he missed all the action.

573
00:43:40,910 --> 00:43:43,579
有什么好担心的  庄哥 一定会有机会让你对付他们
Don't worry, John. You'll get your chance to deal with the Indians.

574
00:43:43,746 --> 00:43:47,333
是啊！到时候我们联手 叫他们吃不了  兜着走
Yeah. We'll take care of them, like we did last time, eh, mates?

575
00:43:47,500 --> 00:43:49,961
来一个我们就杀一个
We shot ourselves an injun

576
00:43:50,127 --> 00:43:51,879
来两个…
Or maybe two or three

577
00:43:52,046 --> 00:43:54,507
别唱了  比杀猪还难听 干活去
All right, you howling nutter, get to work.

578
00:43:54,674 --> 00:43:57,385
拜托！  阿宾  苦中作乐都不行啊
Come on, Ben. It's just a little fun.

579
00:43:57,552 --> 00:44:00,179
说得没错  我们是够苦了
Sure! We're having loads of fun, right?

580
00:44:00,346 --> 00:44:02,181
你看看我们 既没金子  又没得吃
Look at us. No gold, no food,

581
00:44:02,348 --> 00:44:06,727
所有的好处  全让那个死胖子 雷利夫  一个人占尽了
while Ratcliffe sits up in his tent all day, happy as a clam.

582
00:44:07,520 --> 00:44:09,188
怎么搞的？
I'm doomed!

583
00:44:09,355 --> 00:44:13,276
这时候我应该坐拥万金啊 却连金沙都找不到
I should be wallowing in riches by now, and I haven't found as much as a speck.

584
00:44:13,442 --> 00:44:18,239
想一想  想一想 一定就藏在这附近
Think. Think! It's got to be around here somewhere.

585
00:44:19,574 --> 00:44:21,200
究竟在哪？
Where could it be?

586
00:44:22,702 --> 00:44:28,207
我已经把这附近的地方 统统挖过了  都没有
I've mined the forests and the hills and the swamps... and nothing!

587
00:44:31,043 --> 00:44:34,297
怎么会没有？我漏掉了什么？
Why can't I find it? What am I overlooking?

588
00:44:35,882 --> 00:44:39,677
我…我自己做的
I... I... I made it myself!

589
00:44:39,969 --> 00:44:41,679
把它给我拿下来
Take that silly...

590
00:44:42,555 --> 00:44:44,765
对了  印第安鬼
Of course. The Indians.

591
00:44:44,932 --> 00:44:48,352
华根  你说印第安鬼 为什么要来袭击我们？
Wiggins, why do you think those insolent heathens attacked us?

592
00:44:48,519 --> 00:44:51,772
因为我们侵入他们的领土 还有砍树挖地吗？
We invaded their land, cut down their trees and dug up their earth?

593
00:44:51,939 --> 00:44:56,527
是黄金  是他们故意把黄金 藏起来不让我们找到
It's the gold! They have it, and they don't want us to take it from them.

594
00:44:56,694 --> 00:45:00,239
那就只有逼我动用武力去抢
Well, I'll just have to take it by force then, won't I?

595
00:45:02,241 --> 00:45:05,077
你们  庄上尉哪儿去了？
You there! Where's Captain Smith?

596
00:45:05,244 --> 00:45:09,749
他…走了 对  他早就被你吓跑了
- Well, he's... gone. - Aye. Your singing scared him off.

597
00:45:09,916 --> 00:45:13,294
那就找他去  站在这儿干嘛 要是碰到印第安鬼该怎么办？
- Go get him, for heaven's sake! - What ifwe run into the Indians?

598
00:45:13,461 --> 00:45:16,255
难道就不会用你的枪吗？
That's what guns are for.

599
00:45:16,422 --> 00:45:18,424
带上家伙立刻出发
Now arm yourselves and get moving!

600
00:45:43,950 --> 00:45:45,826
宝嘉康蒂
Pocahontas.

601
00:45:46,786 --> 00:45:48,829
你应该留在部族里的
You should be inside the village.

602
00:45:48,996 --> 00:45:50,331
我们正忙着呢
We'll be all right.

603
00:45:50,498 --> 00:45:53,668
勇士们快要到了 我们在准备粮食
We're gathering food for when the warriors arrive.

604
00:45:53,834 --> 00:45:54,877
别走远
Don't go far.

605
00:45:55,044 --> 00:45:58,381
这种时刻可不能再乱跑了 知道了  爸
- Now is not the time to be running off. - Yes, Father.

606
00:45:59,882 --> 00:46:04,095
看你挂上这条项链 就跟你妈一个模样
When I see you wear that necklace, you lookjust like your mother.

607
00:46:05,012 --> 00:46:06,597
我好想她哦
I miss her.

608
00:46:06,764 --> 00:46:08,891
她仍然伴着我们
But she is still with us.

609
00:46:09,058 --> 00:46:13,312
每当风吹过树林 我都感觉得到她的存在
Whenever the wind moves through the trees, I feel her presence.

610
00:46:13,479 --> 00:46:16,190
她是我们族人 智慧和力量的象征
Our people look to her for wisdom and strength.

611
00:46:16,357 --> 00:46:18,985
将来他们要看你的
Someday, they will look to you as well.

612
00:46:19,151 --> 00:46:20,778
我不会让他们失望的
I would be honored by that.

613
00:46:21,862 --> 00:46:23,698
你不该单独在这里
You shouldn't be out here alone.

614
00:46:23,864 --> 00:46:27,243
我叫高刚来 好了  是什么？
- I'll send for Kocoum. - All right, what is it?

615
00:46:27,410 --> 00:46:28,869
什么？ 你心里头有鬼
- What? - You're hiding something.

616
00:46:29,036 --> 00:46:30,871
我哪里有什么鬼呀
I'm not hiding anything.

617
00:46:31,038 --> 00:46:33,040
宝嘉康蒂  你告诉我  我保证
Pocahontas, you can tell me. I promise.

618
00:46:33,207 --> 00:46:37,211
我绝对不会告诉别人的 宝嘉康蒂  你看
I won't tell anyone... Pocahontas, look!

619
00:46:40,673 --> 00:46:44,218
是个白人！我要去通知… 你来这儿干什么？
- It's one of them! I'm going to get... - What are you doing here?

620
00:46:44,385 --> 00:46:46,262
我要来看你呀
I had to see you again.

621
00:46:46,429 --> 00:46:51,392
宝嘉康蒂  宝嘉康蒂 拜托  你什么都别说
- Pocahontas! Pocahontas! - Please! Don't say anything.

622
00:46:51,559 --> 00:46:52,893
快！跟我来！
Quick! This way!

623
00:46:53,060 --> 00:46:54,645
可是… 尼可曼
- But... - Nakoma.

624
00:46:54,812 --> 00:46:59,108
宝嘉康蒂人呢？ 我…我没看见她
- Where is Pocahontas? - I haven't seen her.

625
00:47:00,401 --> 00:47:04,238
她不能老是到处乱跑 这样子是非常危险的
Pocahontas can't keep running off. It's dangerous out there.

626
00:47:04,405 --> 00:47:07,491
劝劝她  她都听你的
Tell her that. She listens to you.

627
00:47:10,202 --> 00:47:11,746
哼  她才不呢
Sure she does.

628
00:47:27,887 --> 00:47:29,930
真是世外桃源
This place is incredible.

629
00:47:30,097 --> 00:47:33,225
可是我们那班人 只是想着来挖黄金
And to think we came all this way Just to dig it up for gold.

630
00:47:33,392 --> 00:47:35,144
黄金？ 嗨  米糕
- Gold? - Hey, Meeko.

631
00:47:35,311 --> 00:47:39,106
什么黄金啊？ 黄金就是黄黄的
- What's gold? - You know, it's yellow.

632
00:47:39,273 --> 00:47:41,317
从地下出来  很值钱的
It comes out of the ground. It's really valuable.

633
00:47:42,276 --> 00:47:43,277
在这儿  我们有好多哦
Here, we have lots of it.

634
00:47:44,236 --> 00:47:45,613
黄金
Gold.

635
00:47:45,780 --> 00:47:49,950
不是这个  这个才是  黄金
No, no! Gold is this.

636
00:47:50,117 --> 00:47:52,119
这里没有这种东西
There's nothing like that around here.

637
00:47:52,286 --> 00:47:54,955
没有？ 我没见过
- No gold? - Not that I've seen.

638
00:47:56,248 --> 00:47:57,625
如果他们知道
All this way for nothing.

639
00:47:57,792 --> 00:48:00,461
这里没有黄金的话 一定很失望
Those boys are in for a big surprise.

640
00:48:00,628 --> 00:48:02,880
他们会走吗？ 有些会吧
- Will they leave? - Some of them might.

641
00:48:05,382 --> 00:48:06,425
你也回家？
Will you go home?

642
00:48:06,592 --> 00:48:09,887
我一向是到处流浪  四海为家
Well, it's not like I have much of a home to go back to.

643
00:48:10,054 --> 00:48:12,306
回不回去也无所谓
I've never really belonged anywhere.

644
00:48:12,640 --> 00:48:14,809
那你留下来
You could belong here.

645
00:48:24,151 --> 00:48:25,402
这是什么？
What was that?

646
00:48:25,569 --> 00:48:29,782
你看见什么了？ 没有  没有  我只是…
- Did you see something? - No, no. I just...

647
00:48:29,949 --> 00:48:32,868
我真的没有看到东西 怎么了？
I didn't see anything. Did I?

648
00:48:33,035 --> 00:48:34,703
再看哪
Look again.

649
00:48:35,871 --> 00:48:38,707
让声音轻轻地告诉你
Let it break upon you

650
00:48:38,874 --> 00:48:43,546
人生真谛
Like a wave upon the sand

651
00:48:45,089 --> 00:48:47,299
你好  庄迈斯
Hello, John Smith.

652
00:48:47,466 --> 00:48:50,302
宝嘉康蒂  树在跟我说话？
Pocahontas, that tree is talking to me.

653
00:48:50,469 --> 00:48:52,429
那你快回话啊
Then you should talk back.

654
00:48:52,596 --> 00:48:54,473
不要怕呀  小伙子
Don't be frightened, young man.

655
00:48:54,640 --> 00:48:57,184
我可不会咬人的
My bark is worse than my bite.

656
00:48:58,936 --> 00:49:02,273
说话呀 跟树要说什么？
- Say something. - What do you say to a tree?

657
00:49:02,440 --> 00:49:04,859
什么都可以
Anything you want.

658
00:49:08,028 --> 00:49:12,116
好啊  你好 走过来  庄迈斯
- So... - Come closer, John Smith.

659
00:49:13,367 --> 00:49:17,621
他心肠挺好的  长得好帅呀
He has a good soul. And he's handsome, too!

660
00:49:17,788 --> 00:49:20,958
我喜欢她 我知道你会
- Oh, I like her. - I knew you would.

661
00:49:21,125 --> 00:49:24,545
迈斯  迈斯  你在哪儿啊？
Smith! Smith, where are you, mate?

662
00:49:24,712 --> 00:49:27,214
不要让他们看到 快  到这儿来
- We can't let them see us. - Quick! Over here.

663
00:49:27,381 --> 00:49:31,093
这个地方好吓人啊 那些蛮夷可能就躲在附近
This place gives me the creeps. Savages could be hiding anywhere.

664
00:49:31,260 --> 00:49:35,473
怕什么 让我看见  二话不说开枪
If you spot one, don't ask questions. Just shoot.

665
00:49:37,558 --> 00:49:41,187
你干什么绊我啊？ 不是我  是那棵树
- Watch your feet, you big oaf! - It wasn't me! It was the tree.

666
00:49:41,353 --> 00:49:44,857
是啊  是那棵树抬起脚 把我给绊倒的
Of course! The tree just felt like lifting its roots...

667
00:49:48,110 --> 00:49:49,653
我们快离开这儿吧
Let's get out of here.

668
00:49:51,947 --> 00:49:54,158
快跑 那庄迈斯怎么办呢？
- Run! - But what about Smith?

669
00:49:54,325 --> 00:49:57,077
别管他了  他会照顾自己的
He's a big lad, he can take care of himself!

670
00:49:57,244 --> 00:49:58,412
还好没有跟你作对
I'm glad you're on our side.

671
00:49:58,579 --> 00:50:01,540
这几条老筋还挺管用的呢
There's still some snap in these old vines.

672
00:50:01,707 --> 00:50:04,376
我先回去了 不然他们会全部出来找我
I better get back before they send the whole camp after me.

673
00:50:04,543 --> 00:50:08,339
什么时候再见啊？ 今天晚上  在这儿
- When will I see you again? - Meet me tonight, right here.

674
00:50:13,552 --> 00:50:18,224
哇  这两百年来 都没碰过这么兴奋的事情
Well! I haven't had this much excitement in 200 years.

675
00:50:18,390 --> 00:50:21,435
