Perhaps it's your dream.

680
00:50:32,446 --> 00:50:37,535
我的梦？柳树婆婆  你说那支箭 所指的会不会就是他？
My dream? Do you think he's the one the spinning arrow was pointing to?

681
00:50:46,627 --> 00:50:48,379
勇士们来了
The warriors are here.

682
00:51:00,057 --> 00:51:02,768
宝嘉康蒂  你疯了 跟那个白人混在一起
Pocahontas, are you crazy? What were you doing with one of them?

683
00:51:02,935 --> 00:51:04,228
你在这儿 高刚
- There you are! - Kocoum!

684
00:51:04,395 --> 00:51:08,482
你看看  现在人强马壮 一定能把白鬼赶尽杀绝
Look at them! Now we have enough warriors to destroy those white demons!

685
00:51:10,484 --> 00:51:14,780
团结起各部族的力量 我们一定能打败敌人
Now that we are joined by our brothers, we will defeat this enemy.

686
00:51:22,496 --> 00:51:24,081
爸  我有话要跟你说
Father, I need to speak with you.

687
00:51:24,248 --> 00:51:26,834
现在不行  乖女儿 联盟正在集会
Not now, my daughter. The council is gathering.

688
00:51:27,001 --> 00:51:30,337
不一定非要开战啊 一定有更好的方法
We don't have to fight them. There must be a better way.

689
00:51:30,504 --> 00:51:33,132
这个时候 已经由不得我们选择了
Sometimes our paths are chosen for us.

690
00:51:33,299 --> 00:51:35,843
也许你该去跟他们谈一谈
But maybe we should try talking to them.

691
00:51:36,010 --> 00:51:37,428
他们不会想谈的
They do not want to talk.

692
00:51:37,594 --> 00:51:41,265
如果他们真的愿意谈呢？ 你会听他们说吗？你会吗？
But if one of them did want to talk, you would listen to him, wouldn't you?

693
00:51:41,432 --> 00:51:43,350
宝嘉康蒂 你会吗？
- Pocahontas... - Wouldn't you?

694
00:51:43,517 --> 00:51:47,688
我当然会了 但怎么会那么简单
Of course I would, but it is not that simple.

695
00:51:47,855 --> 00:51:50,357
事情已经不再单纯了
Nothing is simple anymore.

696
00:52:34,610 --> 00:52:36,528
慢着  汤姆斯  是我
Easy, Thomas, it's me.

697
00:52:37,529 --> 00:52:42,034
庄哥  我差点就开枪了 你根本没有瞄准目标
- Oh, John! I could've killed you. - Not aiming like that, you couldn't.

698
00:52:42,201 --> 00:52:45,245
开枪的时候两眼睁开 才看得更清楚
Keep both eyes open when you shoot. You'll see twice as well.

699
00:52:46,914 --> 00:52:50,125
迈斯  回来了 我们一直在到处找你
- Smith! There you are. - We were looking all over for you.

700
00:52:50,292 --> 00:52:53,420
迈斯  你跑哪儿去了？
Smith! Where have you been?

701
00:52:53,587 --> 00:52:56,131
大人  我到周围查看一下而已
I was out scouting the terrain, sir.

702
00:52:56,298 --> 00:52:58,675
很好  那你一定 对印第安鬼了若指掌了
Excellent. Then you must know the Indians' whereabouts.

703
00:52:58,842 --> 00:53:00,761
要开战就该知己知彼
We'll need that information for the battle.

704
00:53:00,928 --> 00:53:03,180
开战？ 我们一定要把这些蛮夷
- What battle? - We will eliminate these savages

705
00:53:03,347 --> 00:53:06,141
赶尽杀绝 不行  你不能这样做
- once and for all. - No! You can't do that!

706
00:53:07,184 --> 00:53:11,688
噢  不能？ 对  我们用不着打他们
- Oh, can't I? - Look. We don't have to fight them.

707
00:53:11,855 --> 00:53:13,732
庄哥  这什么意思？ 我遇上他们
- John, what's gotten into you? - I met one of them.

708
00:53:13,899 --> 00:53:16,110
什么？ 遇上蛮夷了？
- You what? - A savage?

709
00:53:16,276 --> 00:53:18,946
他们不是蛮夷  他们能帮助我们
They're not savages. They can help us.

710
00:53:19,113 --> 00:53:22,533
他们熟悉土地 懂得如何测定河道
They know the land. They know how to navigate the rivers.

711
00:53:23,117 --> 00:53:25,661
你看  是粮食 这是什么东西？
- And look. It's food. - What is it?

712
00:53:25,828 --> 00:53:27,955
比饼乾跟燕麦粥好吃多了
It's better than hardtack and gruel, that's for sure.

713
00:53:28,122 --> 00:53:29,123
燕麦粥好
I like gruel.

714
00:53:29,289 --> 00:53:31,834
他们才不会要请客吃饭
They don't want to feed us, you ninnies!

715
00:53:32,000 --> 00:53:34,294
他们要杀人  杀我们
They want to kill us! All of us!

716
00:53:34,461 --> 00:53:37,423
为了独霸黄金 他们用上好多诡计
They've got our gold, and they'll do anything to keep it!

717
00:53:37,589 --> 00:53:41,093
这里根本就没有黄金 没有黄金？
- But there is no gold. - No gold?

718
00:53:41,802 --> 00:53:45,305
我看是你的那位 印第安朋友告诉你的吧？
And I suppose your little Indian friend told you this?

719
00:53:45,472 --> 00:53:46,807
是的
Yes.

720
00:53:46,974 --> 00:53:50,561
撒谎  撒谎  全都撒谎 凶险的小偷
Lies. Lies! All of it! Murderous thieves.

721
00:53:50,728 --> 00:53:52,771
我们文明社会 不容许这种贼存在
There's no room for their kind in civilized society.

722
00:53:52,938 --> 00:53:54,231
可是这里是他们的土地！
But this is their land!

723
00:53:54,398 --> 00:53:57,651
这里是我的  我就是法律
This is my land! I make the laws here.

724
00:53:57,818 --> 00:54:01,989
听清楚  要是任何一个人 见到印第安鬼
And I say anyone who so much as looks at an Indian

725
00:54:02,156 --> 00:54:07,494
而不杀他的话 就等于是造反  要问罪
without killing him on sight will be tried for treason and hanged.

726
00:54:12,458 --> 00:54:13,834
宝嘉康蒂
Pocahontas!

727
00:54:14,001 --> 00:54:15,669
尼可曼 不要再去了
- Nakoma. - Don't go out there.

728
00:54:15,836 --> 00:54:19,089
我已经为你撒过谎 你不能一错再错啊
I lied for you once, don't ask me to do it again.

729
00:54:19,256 --> 00:54:20,674
我一定要去
I have to do this.

730
00:54:20,841 --> 00:54:22,885
他是白人 你不了解
- He's one of them! - You don't know him.

731
00:54:23,051 --> 00:54:25,846
你去见他 就等于背叛自己的族人
If you go out there, you'll be turning your back on your own people.

732
00:54:26,013 --> 00:54:28,307
我这么做是要帮助我的族人
I'm trying to help my people.

733
00:54:28,474 --> 00:54:31,602
宝嘉康蒂  不要去 你是我的好朋友
Pocahontas, please, you're my best friend.

734
00:54:31,768 --> 00:54:33,395
我不要你受到伤害
I don't want you to get hurt.

735
00:54:33,562 --> 00:54:37,441
放心  我不会有事的 宝嘉康蒂  不要！
- I won't. I know what I'm doing. - Pocahontas, no!

736
00:54:44,072 --> 00:54:46,867
雷利夫 不会真叫我们空手而回吧
Ratcliffe wouldn't take us halfway around the world for nothing.

737
00:54:47,034 --> 00:54:50,329
如果迈斯是对的 如果这里真的是没有黄金
But what if Smith is right? What if there is no gold?

738
00:54:50,496 --> 00:54:53,624
你是说雷利夫一直在欺骗我们
If you ask me, Ratcliffe's been lying to us since we left London.

739
00:54:53,790 --> 00:54:55,626
瞧你说的  你们这群笨蛋
Listen to you, you bunch of idiots.

740
00:54:55,793 --> 00:54:58,128
如果什么都没有 那些蛮夷才不会攻击我们
Those savages didn't attack us for nothing.

741
00:54:58,295 --> 00:54:59,880
他们一定藏着一些东西
They're hiding something.

742
00:55:00,047 --> 00:55:03,383
要是真的有黄金 我们就得跟他们拼命了
If they do have the gold, I reckon we'll have to fight them.

743
00:55:03,550 --> 00:55:06,053
我不会  我才不会冒着危险… 不是太热就是太冷
- Not me. I'm not risking my neck... - Either too hot or too cold.

744
00:55:06,220 --> 00:55:08,722
自从来了这里 我就一直感到不安
I haven't been comfortable since we got here.

745
00:55:09,890 --> 00:55:12,392
我也觉得浑身不自在
Me, too. I'm itching a lot.

746
00:55:19,441 --> 00:55:21,860
跟踪他 是  总督大人
- Follow him. - Yes, Governor.

747
00:55:22,027 --> 00:55:24,321
我要知道他究竟去哪里？
I want to know where he's sneaking off to.

748
00:55:24,488 --> 00:55:27,491
是  大人 如果遇见印第安鬼
- Yes, sir. - If you happen to see any Indians...

749
00:55:28,492 --> 00:55:29,993
就开枪
...shoot them.

750
00:55:33,664 --> 00:55:36,375
还有  汤姆斯 你无论当水手
And, Thomas, you've been a slipshod sailor

751
00:55:36,542 --> 00:55:38,919
和军人的表现都不怎么样
and a poor excuse for a soldier.

752
00:55:39,086 --> 00:55:41,380
别再叫我失望了
Don't disappoint me again.

753
00:55:51,807 --> 00:55:53,642
高刚 什么事？
- Kocoum. - What is it?

754
00:55:54,601 --> 00:55:58,355
宝嘉康蒂她… 怎么了？她怎么了？
- It's Pocahontas. - What's wrong? Is she all right?

755
00:56:00,399 --> 00:56:02,317
我想她遇上了麻烦
I think she's in trouble.

756
00:56:06,989 --> 00:56:09,950
大地在发抖啊  孩子 出了什么事了？
The earth is trembling, child. What's happened?

757
00:56:10,117 --> 00:56:11,451
勇士们都来了
The warriors are here.

758
00:56:11,618 --> 00:56:13,579
宝嘉康蒂 迈斯
- Pocahontas. - John!

759
00:56:14,788 --> 00:56:18,542
你听我说 我们的人正准备攻打你们
Listen to me. My men are planning to attack your people.

760
00:56:18,709 --> 00:56:19,710
你们一定要小心
You've got to warn them.

761
00:56:19,877 --> 00:56:22,004
也许现在还来得及阻止他
Maybe it's not too late to stop this.

762
00:56:22,170 --> 00:56:24,214
你得要跟我去和我爸爸谈一谈
You have to come with me and talk to my father.

763
00:56:24,381 --> 00:56:26,925
宝嘉康蒂 我看谈也是于事无补的
Pocahontas, talking isn't going to do any good.

764
00:56:27,092 --> 00:56:28,760
我已经跟我的人谈过了
I already tried talking to my men,

765
00:56:28,927 --> 00:56:31,221
他们简直就是无药可救
but everything about this land has them spooked.

766
00:56:35,726 --> 00:56:38,020
我从来没有见过那样的怪物
That's the strangest creature I've ever seen!

767
00:56:42,232 --> 00:56:43,817
波斯？
Percy?

768
00:56:46,236 --> 00:56:48,906
放松  波斯！过来 米糕  回来
- Easy, Percy! Come here! - Meeko, come back!

769
00:56:49,072 --> 00:56:51,742
你都看到了  两边如果拼上了 怎么能挡得住呢？
You see what I mean? Once two sides want to fight, nothing can stop them.

770
00:56:51,909 --> 00:56:55,078
好了  你们两个 没事  他是朋友
- Come here, both of you! - It's all right. He's a friend.

771
00:56:55,245 --> 00:56:56,413
坏坏狗  给我坐下
Bad! Bad dog! Sit!

772
00:56:58,790 --> 00:57:01,376
米糕  你在干什么？ 波斯  不要再闹了
- What are you doing? Meeko! - Percy, get back here!

773
00:57:01,543 --> 00:57:05,547
你在干什么？停啊 够了  我受够了
- What are you doing? Stop that! - All right, that's enough!

774
00:57:12,471 --> 00:57:14,973
这就够让你们筋疲力尽了
It's enough to make your sap boil.

775
00:57:16,475 --> 00:57:20,729
现在我要让你们看些东西  看啊
Now then, there's something I want to show you. Look!

776
00:57:24,816 --> 00:57:28,028
是涟漪 什么意思？
- The ripples. - What about them?

777
00:57:28,195 --> 00:57:32,741
开始小小的  然后越来越大
So small at first, then look how they grow.

778
00:57:34,034 --> 00:57:36,787
可得要有人先开始哦
But someone has to start them.

779
00:57:37,412 --> 00:57:38,956
他们是不会听我们的了
They're not going to listen to us.

780
00:57:39,122 --> 00:57:43,335
小伙子 正确的路都是不容易走的
Young man, sometimes the right path is not the easiest one.

781
00:57:43,502 --> 00:57:45,170
知道吗？
Don't you see?

782
00:57:45,337 --> 00:57:49,633
你们要在一起 就一定要他们停战
Only when the fighting stops can you be together.

783
00:57:53,637 --> 00:57:56,264
好吧  我们去见你爸爸
All right. Let's go talk to your father.

784
00:58:32,592 --> 00:58:34,761
高刚  不要！
Kocoum, no!

785
00:58:41,393 --> 00:58:42,978
高刚
Kocoum!

786
00:58:46,106 --> 00:58:47,357
你放开他
Leave him alone!

787
00:59:03,790 --> 00:59:05,876
高刚  住手
Kocoum, stop!

788
00:59:08,253 --> 00:59:10,338
两眼睁开
Both eyes open.

789
00:59:18,638 --> 00:59:21,308
汤姆斯 中了…
- Thomas! - Is he...

790
00:59:21,475 --> 00:59:23,226
你杀了他
You killed him.

791
00:59:23,393 --> 00:59:25,228
我以为… 走开  你走开
- I thought that... - Get away from him!

792
00:59:25,395 --> 00:59:27,481
宝嘉康蒂  不要 他只是想…
Pocahontas, it won't help! He was only...

793
00:59:27,647 --> 00:59:28,648
他杀了他
He killed him!

794
00:59:30,149 --> 00:59:31,984
Get all the wagons...

795
00:59:32,152 --> 00:59:35,739
汤姆斯  快点离开 快点走啊
Thomas, get out of here! Get out of here!

796
01:00:39,469 --> 01:00:40,846
是谁干的？
Who did this?

797
01:00:41,012 --> 01:00:42,973
宝嘉康蒂跑到树林里
Pocahontas was out in the woods.

798
01:00:43,140 --> 01:00:46,059
高刚跟去找她 这个白人袭击他
Kocoum went to find her and this white man attacked them.

799
01:00:47,853 --> 01:00:52,899
你的武器很厉害 可是敌不上我们的愤怒
Your weapons are strong, but now our anger is stronger.

800
01:00:53,066 --> 01:00:56,486
到日出时刻  第一个先处决他 可是爸…
- At sunrise, he'll be the first to die! - But Father!

801
01:00:57,154 --> 01:01:00,031
我叫你留在部族里头
I told you to stay in the village.

802
01:01:00,198 --> 01:01:02,033
你就是不听
You disobeyed me.

803
01:01:02,200 --> 01:01:05,829
你让你爸爸丢脸 我只是想要帮助大家
- You have shamed your father! - I was only trying to help.

804
01:01:05,996 --> 01:01:09,916
就因为你的无知 高刚牺牲了
Because of your foolishness, Kocoum is dead!

805
01:01:10,083 --> 01:01:11,877
把他带走
Take him away!

806
01:01:26,474 --> 01:01:28,643
高刚全是为了要保护我
Kocoum was just coming to protect me.

807
01:01:28,810 --> 01:01:32,731
宝嘉康蒂 是我要高刚去的
Pocahontas... I sent Kocoum after you.

808
01:01:34,357 --> 01:01:36,735
我实在很担心你
I was worried about you.

809
01:01:36,902 --> 01:01:39,029
我以为我这样做是对的
I thought I was doing the right thing.

810
01:01:39,195 --> 01:01:42,032
所有的事都因我而起
All this happened because of me.

811
01:01:42,199 --> 01:01:45,285
我再也不能够见到庄迈斯了
And now I'll never see John Smith again.

812
01:01:47,454 --> 01:01:49,080
跟我来
Come with me.

813
01:01:53,585 --> 01:01:57,714
宝嘉康蒂她想要亲自审问 那个杀掉高刚的人
Pocahontas wants to look into the eyes of the man who killed Kocoum.

814
01:02:00,550 --> 01:02:02,135
要快点
Be quick.

815
01:02:20,445 --> 01:02:22,155
宝嘉康蒂
Pocahontas.

816
01:02:24,658 --> 01:02:28,119
我很抱歉 为什么？这个啊？
- I'm so sorry. - For what? This?

817
01:02:28,286 --> 01:02:30,622
我受过比这个还重的伤
I've gotten out of worse scrapes than this.

818
01:02:30,789 --> 01:02:32,249
现在可想不起来
Can't think of any right now, but...

819
01:02:32,415 --> 01:02:34,251
如果我们从没遇到过多好
It would've been better ifwe'd never met.

820
01:02:34,417 --> 01:02:38,713
什么都不会发生了 宝嘉康蒂  你看着我
- None of this would've happened. - Pocahontas, look at me.

821
01:02:39,798 --> 01:02:44,552
我情愿明天死掉 也不要长命百岁而不认识你
I'd rather die tomorrow than live a hundred years without knowing you.

822
01:02:45,595 --> 01:02:48,640
宝嘉康蒂 我不能没有你
- Pocahontas. - I can't leave you.

823
01:02:48,807 --> 01:02:50,183
绝对不会
You never will.

824
01:02:50,350 --> 01:02:55,063
无论我发生什么事 我都与你同在  直到永远
No matter what happens to me, I'll always be with you. Forever.

825
01:03:08,118 --> 01:03:11,454
快呀  大家快来呀
Help! Somebody help! Help!

826
01:03:11,621 --> 01:03:13,206
快呀 你别急呀  兄弟  有什么事啊？
- Help! - Easy, lad. What is it?

827
01:03:13,373 --> 01:03:14,874
是庄迈斯  他被抓了
It's Smith! They got him!

828
01:03:15,041 --> 01:03:17,210
被谁抓了？ 蛮夷！
- Who got him? - The savages!

829
01:03:17,377 --> 01:03:19,087
蛮夷？ 把他绑起来  带走了
- Savages? - They captured him! Dragged him off!

830
01:03:19,254 --> 01:03:20,880
往哪儿去了？ 往北边去了
- Where'd they take him? - They headed north.

831
01:03:21,047 --> 01:03:23,091
有多少人啊？ 不清楚  起码十几个
- How many were there? - I don't know. At least a dozen.

832
01:03:23,258 --> 01:03:25,385
肮脏的野兽！
Filthy beasts!

833
01:03:25,552 --> 01:03:29,347
这当然是对的  华根 我这是得来全不费功夫
It's perfect, Wiggins! I couldn't have planned this better myself.

834
01:03:29,514 --> 01:03:32,392
黄金全是我的了
The gold is as good as mine.

835
01:03:32,559 --> 01:03:35,228
把他救回来 不能丢下他不管啊
We've got to save him! He'd do the same for any of us.

836
01:03:35,395 --> 01:03:37,731
他说得对  我们一定要去救他
Thomas is right! We've got to do something.

837
01:03:37,897 --> 01:03:42,569
那当然了  我早就说 蛮夷是绝对不可以相信的
And so we shall. I told you those savages couldn't be trusted.

838
01:03:42,736 --> 01:03:45,947
庄迈斯相信他们 他们是怎么对他的？
Smith tried to befriend them, and look what they've done to him!

839
01:03:46,406 --> 01:03:49,909
我们一定要尽全力 把我们的好兄弟救回来
But now I say it's time to rescue our courageous comrade.

840
01:03:50,076 --> 01:03:52,287
天一亮  我们就出击！
At daybreak, we attack!

841
01:03:53,913 --> 01:03:57,125
你怎么会知道 会遇到这一群人？
What can you expect from filthy little heathens?

842
01:03:57,292 --> 01:04:00,378
全都是令人恶心的家伙
Here's what you get when races are diverse

843
01:04:00,545 --> 01:04:02,213
看他们的颜色
Their skin's a hellish red

844
01:04:02,380 --> 01:04:03,840
像火一般炽热
They're only good when dead

845
01:04:04,007 --> 01:04:06,426
是邪恶魔鬼的化身
They're vermin as I said and worse

846
01:04:06,593 --> 01:04:09,346
是野蛮人  野蛮人
They're savages, savages

847
01:04:09,512 --> 01:04:12,515
野蛮不讲道理 野蛮人  野蛮人
- Barely even human - Savages, savages

848
01:04:12,682 --> 01:04:14,267
把他赶走吧
Drive them from our shore!

849
01:04:14,434 --> 01:04:15,935
他们不像我们
They're not like you and me

850
01:04:16,102 --> 01:04:17,729
野蛮又不讲道理
Which means they must be evil

851
01:04:17,896 --> 01:04:20,607
我们要提高警惕
We must sound the drums ofwar

852
01:04:20,774 --> 01:04:22,734
是野蛮人  野蛮人
They're savages, savages

853
01:04:22,901 --> 01:04:24,611
野蛮不讲道理
Dirty, shrieking devils

854
01:04:24,778 --> 01:04:28,573
我们用心来对抗
Now we sound the drums ofwar

855
01:04:33,244 --> 01:04:34,871
你可曾知道
This is what we feared

856
01:04:35,038 --> 01:04:36,748
贪得无厌的欲望
The paleface is a demon

857
01:04:36,915 --> 01:04:39,793
